test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x78115deb19c0>([74])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x78115deb19c0> = [[1, 74, 1, 74], [1, 74, 1, 74], [74, 1, 74], [74, 1, 74], [1, 74, 1, 74], [1, 74, 1, 74], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 5476 == 74
 +  where 5476 = <built-in function prod>([1, 2, 37, 74])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
